      "solution": "n = gets.to_i\nlength = 0\n\npoints = n.times.map{gets.split.map(&:to_i)}\npoints<< points[0] if points.size>2\n\npoints.each_cons(2){|a,b|length+=Math.sqrt((b[0]-a[0])**2+(b[1]-a[1])**2)}\n\nputs (length+0.5).to_i",
